item.description: Federal Risk and Authorization Management Program (FedRAMP) Profile Examples The following representations of the “High”, “Moderate” and “Low” baselines (profiles) are derived from source data defined by FedRAMP: FedRAMP High Security Controls FedRAMP MODERATE Security Controls FedRAMP LOW Security Controls Machine made OSCAL Profile versions: FedRAMP HIGH Baseline OSCAL Profile FedRAMP MODERATE Baseline OSCAL Profile FedRAMP LOW Baseline OSCAL Profile JSON versions are also available for the OSCAL profiles above containing equivalent content.
